    "Moreover, the negative sign of the estimated parameter shows that an increase in global financial stress leads to a decrease in AMIM values.",
    "However, the results show that AMIM is significantly and positively affected by the MSCI world stock market only when the Bitcoin market is efficient (low quantiles of the order 0.2).",
    "Additionally, we found that investment substitutes have an insignificant effect on AMIM.",
    "A plausible explanation for this finding is that investors look at substitutes such as gold and crude oil to hedge their portfolios.",
    "Policy uncertainty measured by EPU and VIX was found to have no significant effect on the efficiency of Bitcoin, indicating that Bitcoin market efficiency is not influenced by economic or market uncertainty."
